  "data": {
    "name": "Rule of Thumb",
    "description": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "A rule that holds true for all normal members of a class, but admits exceptions. A rule of thumb is one that usually works in most situations, but may fail occasionally. The advantage of rules of thumb is that they are usually simpler and easier to use than universal rules that always work.",
